  "texts": [
    "The TIMIT dataset contains acoustic speech signals of sentences spoken by 630 speakers from 8 major dialect regions of the United States.",
    "The goal of the tasks is to recognize the phonemes of every 10ms frame in each sentence.",
    "We follow the experimental settings of a prior work 33.",
    "The training, validation, and testing sets contain 3,696, 400, and 192 sequences, respectively.",
    "The performance is evaluated on the core testing set."
  ],
